01:09:18.938 --> 01:09:22.838
to accomplish what needs to be known to

01:09:22.998 --> 01:09:25.619
validate or invalidate Paul,

01:09:26.199 --> 01:09:29.320
we must examine and carefully consider the

01:09:29.360 --> 01:09:32.622
Torah and juxtaposition what Paul said

01:09:33.582 --> 01:09:34.122
next to it.

01:09:34.985 --> 01:09:35.667
Yeah, it was clear,

01:09:36.207 --> 01:09:38.850
revealing that no one is authorized to add

01:09:38.890 --> 01:09:40.652
to or subtract from his Torah.

01:09:40.712 --> 01:09:43.354
So if you negate it, you're a liar.

01:09:44.956 --> 01:09:47.177
If we witness the Torah's role in our

01:09:47.217 --> 01:09:49.140
lives being diminished by anyone like

01:09:49.180 --> 01:09:49.579
Paul,

01:09:50.121 --> 01:09:52.783
or we find a writer adding something new

01:09:52.823 --> 01:09:55.386
to it, like the rabbis and the Talmud,

01:09:57.103 --> 01:09:58.886
More like a new covenant.

01:09:59.067 --> 01:10:01.452
We should be careful because such a person

01:10:01.652 --> 01:10:03.194
is not speaking for God,

01:10:03.274 --> 01:10:06.000
even though they're claiming to do so.

01:10:06.060 --> 01:10:07.162
And to bottom thirteen.

01:10:08.112 --> 01:10:10.613
Yahowah reveals that if the prophet stands

01:10:10.712 --> 01:10:14.614
up and establishes himself as Paulos has

01:10:14.694 --> 01:10:16.976
done, he is a false prophet.

01:10:17.577 --> 01:10:19.717
If he claims to have performed miracles as

01:10:19.797 --> 01:10:22.479
Paulos will do, he is a false prophet.

01:10:23.039 --> 01:10:25.161
If he encourages his audience to go after

01:10:25.261 --> 01:10:27.021
other gods by other names,

01:10:27.641 --> 01:10:30.542
like the Romans Gratia or the Greek

01:10:30.743 --> 01:10:32.984
Cheris, whom Paul sponsored,

01:10:33.944 --> 01:10:35.685
even the Iosuchristus,

01:10:36.326 --> 01:10:37.447
he is a false prophet.

01:10:38.087 --> 01:10:39.847
If he promotes religious worship,

01:10:40.248 --> 01:10:42.930
which is the result of Paulos' letters,

01:10:43.229 --> 01:10:44.411
he is a false prophet.

01:10:45.032 --> 01:10:47.613
If his writings fail to affirm his love

01:10:47.653 --> 01:10:48.974
and respect for Yahowah ,

01:10:49.675 --> 01:10:51.216
when he does not even know him,

01:10:51.275 --> 01:10:52.436
he is a false prophet.

01:10:53.377 --> 01:10:55.998
And that is a problem for Paulos,

01:10:56.458 --> 01:10:59.081
because he implies that Yahowah is

01:10:59.261 --> 01:11:03.944
incompetent, impotent, oh, and far,

01:11:04.024 --> 01:11:04.805
far worse.

01:11:05.975 --> 01:11:06.536
In addition,

01:11:06.577 --> 01:11:08.438
a man is a false prophet if he

01:11:08.497 --> 01:11:11.079
encourages anyone to disregard the terms

01:11:11.100 --> 01:11:14.462
and conditions of the Beryth  or the Miqraey 

01:11:14.542 --> 01:11:15.042
of Yahowah ,

01:11:15.063 --> 01:11:16.923
the covenant or the invitations to meet,

01:11:17.344 --> 01:11:19.006
which comprise Yahowah's way.

01:11:19.945 --> 01:11:20.867
And of such prophet,

01:11:20.907 --> 01:11:23.009
God says they are in opposition to him,

01:11:23.048 --> 01:11:24.590
both ruinous and deadly,

01:11:25.170 --> 01:11:27.271
so that we should completely remove their

01:11:27.351 --> 01:11:28.131
disagreeable,

01:11:28.171 --> 01:11:31.033
displeasing and evil corruptions from our

01:11:31.095 --> 01:11:31.454
midst.

01:11:32.556 --> 01:11:35.578
Then in Dabatim, as we are aware,

01:11:35.637 --> 01:11:38.238
Yahowah delineated the six signs of a false

01:11:38.278 --> 01:11:38.677
prophet.

01:11:39.358 --> 01:11:40.778
They claim to speak for him.

01:11:41.219 --> 01:11:41.958
They're arrogant,

01:11:42.038 --> 01:11:43.338
overstepping their bounds.

01:11:43.658 --> 01:11:45.378
Their words are inconsistent with the

01:11:45.418 --> 01:11:46.520
Torah's instructions.

01:11:46.840 --> 01:11:48.920
They recite the names of foreign gods.

01:11:49.199 --> 01:11:51.199
The historical presentations are

01:11:51.279 --> 01:11:53.761
inaccurate and their prophetic promises

01:11:53.801 --> 01:11:55.320
fail to materialize.

01:11:56.341 --> 01:11:59.442
Sha'uwl Paul failed every codicil of this

01:11:59.561 --> 01:11:59.942
test.

01:12:02.136 --> 01:12:07.337
everyone in his opening salvo Paul claimed

01:12:07.377 --> 01:12:09.398
that he did not represent any man or

01:12:09.438 --> 01:12:12.738
any human institution and that would of

01:12:12.779 --> 01:12:15.760
course include the ecclesia which is the

01:12:15.800 --> 01:12:18.461
greek term which has been co-opted to

01:12:18.520 --> 01:12:21.421
represent the christian church and what

01:12:21.521 --> 01:12:22.082
would have

01:12:23.216 --> 01:12:23.856
That, of course,

01:12:23.877 --> 01:12:26.779
would have made Sha'uwl a freelancer,

01:12:26.979 --> 01:12:30.502
an operator on his own recognizance,

01:12:30.561 --> 01:12:32.663
an independent contractor,

01:12:34.664 --> 01:12:37.487
because he did not associate himself even

01:12:37.527 --> 01:12:41.409
with his own ecclesia, church.

01:12:44.311 --> 01:12:46.154
flip side of this admission is also

01:12:46.234 --> 01:12:48.756
problematic if Sha'uwl Paul did not write on

01:12:48.796 --> 01:12:51.037
behalf of what he learned from religious

01:12:51.057 --> 01:12:53.779
teachers in rabbinical school then his

01:12:53.899 --> 01:12:57.563
ubiquitous references to the nomos must

01:12:58.023 --> 01:13:00.645
denote the torah as opposed to the talmud

01:13:01.086 --> 01:13:03.408
this being the case the principal

01:13:03.467 --> 01:13:05.770
methodology used by those who are

01:13:06.465 --> 01:13:08.706
Torah observant to reconcile Paul's

01:13:08.765 --> 01:13:11.447
epistles with Yahowah's word was torn

01:13:11.506 --> 01:13:13.908
asunder by this statement because they all

01:13:13.948 --> 01:13:16.069
claim that Paul was speaking of the

01:13:16.109 --> 01:13:18.131
Talmud, not the Torah,

01:13:18.430 --> 01:13:19.551
when he is negating it.

01:13:19.650 --> 01:13:21.412
But if he is not taught by men,

01:13:21.471 --> 01:13:24.493
he can't be referencing the Talmud,

01:13:24.533 --> 01:13:26.675
could he?

01:13:26.715 --> 01:13:27.654
The facts are evident.

01:13:27.916 --> 01:13:28.836
They're undeniable.

01:13:29.500 --> 01:13:32.242
There is no getting around the realization

01:13:32.282 --> 01:13:35.323
that the nomos is an object of scorn

01:13:35.444 --> 01:13:37.725
and ridicule in this epistle.

01:13:38.367 --> 01:13:40.828
And at no time does Sha'uwl associate the

01:13:40.927 --> 01:13:43.109
nomos with rabbinic law,

01:13:43.449 --> 01:13:45.171
citing Talmudic sources.

01:13:45.712 --> 01:13:47.832
Not once, ever.

01:13:48.533 --> 01:13:49.454
On the contrary,

01:13:49.494 --> 01:13:52.417
his examples and citations are all from

01:13:52.537 --> 01:13:53.136
the Torah,

01:13:53.938 --> 01:13:56.819
clearly identifying the document he is

01:13:56.859 --> 01:13:57.440
assailing.

01:13:58.301 --> 01:13:59.242
And that's a death knell.

01:14:01.252 --> 01:14:03.793
Also convicting,

01:14:04.354 --> 01:14:07.537
if Paulos was speaking for Iusus,

01:14:08.056 --> 01:14:10.920
why didn't he quote him?

01:14:11.000 --> 01:14:13.881
If he was Yahowah's messenger,

01:14:14.381 --> 01:14:17.125
why is Yahowah's word discounted and never

01:14:17.225 --> 01:14:19.426
cited accurately in any one of Paul's

01:14:19.485 --> 01:14:19.867
letters?

01:14:21.247 --> 01:14:23.368
Why, if Paul was speaking for God,

01:14:24.470 --> 01:14:27.972
is his most repeated theme and line,

01:14:29.213 --> 01:14:30.234
but I, Paulos, say?

01:14:32.697 --> 01:14:34.537
If Sha'uwl was Yahowah's apostle,

01:14:36.078 --> 01:14:39.481
why do his letters contradict God?

01:14:43.064 --> 01:14:45.126
Probably a good place for us to conclude

01:14:45.166 --> 01:14:45.805
this program.

